  "original_title": "\u0dc3\u0dde\u0db7\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0dca\u200d\u0dba \u0d9a\u0dbb\u0dcf \u0dba\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0dbd\u0d82\u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0da7 \u0d8b\u0daf\u0dc0\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dbb\u0db1 \u0db6\u0dc0 \u0d87\u0db8\u0dd9\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dc0 \u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "US says it will help Sri Lanka move towards prosperity",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A high level US government delegation visiting Sri Lanka has met President Gotabhaya Rajapaksa and held bilateral discussions.",
        "Mr. Robert Caproth, US Deputy Secretary of State for Asia, Treasury, US Secretary of State for South and Central Asia, Kelly Caderin, and US Ambassador to Sri Lanka, Julie Chung, also called on the President.",
        "Discussions were held on the economic crisis in Sri Lanka. The US delegation told the President that it would extend its long-term support to Sri Lanka in the face of the challenges it is currently facing and will assist Sri Lanka in a prosperous, secure and democratic future."
      ],
